# Wallet Master — architecture (Variant A)

Full plan: `.docs/refactoring.md` (phases, file moves, acceptance criteria).

## Approved `app/` roots

- `Actions/{Domain}/` — use cases, `handle()`, no `Http/Resources`
- `Data/{Domain}/` — DTO, filters, form options (not `ViewModels/`)
- `Http/Controllers|Requests|Resources/{Domain}/` — web layer only
- `Support/{Domain}/` — domain algorithms only (no SDK clients)
- `Integrations/` — Typesense, external APIs (migrating from `Support/Typesense`, `Support/DescriptionMemory`)
- `Imports/` — import workflow and bank adapters (unchanged root)
- `Models/`, `Policies/`, `Jobs/`, `Events/`, `Listeners/`, `Enums/`

Do **not** add `Services/`, `Modules/`, or `ViewModels/` for new code.

## Domain names (always plural in folders)

`Accounts`, `Transactions`, `Transfers`, `Imports`, `Auth`, `Settings`

## Layer rules

| Layer | Does | Does not |
|-------|------|----------|
| Controller | Action → Inertia/redirect, `message_key` toasts | SQL, Resources |
| Action | DB, orchestration, return models/DTO | `*Resource`, `number_format` |
| Resource | Array shape for Inertia | Business rules |
| Data | Filters, form options, result DTOs | Eloquent queries |

## Refactoring PRs

One phase per PR (see `.docs/refactoring.md` §7). Update §10 status table when done. Run `vendor/bin/pint --dirty` and targeted `php artisan test --compact`.
